Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.16,0:02:20.16,apollon main,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,That's all. Just for your information.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.16,0:02:22.66,apollon main,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What are you talkin' about?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.66,0:02:24.08,apollon main,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Don't play dumb.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.83,0:02:26.62,apollon main,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,This has gotten as hard as a rock.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.47,0:02:30.63,apollon main,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,When you think about her, \Nyou get a lump in your throat,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.93,0:02:33.31,apollon main,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,and you can't get the food down, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.40,0:02:36.46,apollon main,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Poor thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.11,0:02:39.10,apollon main,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,You're completely lovesick.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.10,0:02:41.91,apollon main,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,L-Love?! This is love?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.91,0:02:45.30,apollon main,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me you've never fallen in love before?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.30,0:02:46.58,apollon main,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Nope.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.58,0:02:48.10,apollon main,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,You've got to be kidding.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.70,0:02:53.29,apollon main,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Wait. If he really falls for that girl,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.29,0:02:57.83,apollon main,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,then he won't get between Ri and me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.21,0:03:03.70,apollon main,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,All right, we'll skip jazz after school today and meet up to make a game plan instead.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.37,0:03:07.04,sign,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H463C46&\bord0\shad0\fnArmyChalk\fs50\pos(615,168)\frz3.939\frx12\fry358\blur.5}Mikanomachi
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.37,0:03:07.04,sign,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H788BA8&\bord0\shad0\fs40\fscy80\fnBell Gothic Std Light\frz3.845\frx12\fry354\pos(310,344)}End of
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.37,0:03:07.04,sign,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H788BA8&\bord0\shad0\fs40\fscy80\fnBell Gothic Std Light\frx4\fry8\frz5.676\pos(918,317)}Summer \NSale
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.33,0:03:09.22,apollon main,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? At my house?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.22,0:03:11.15,apollon main,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}We ain't goin' to Ri'ko's basement?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.15,0:03:14.40,apollon main,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}You'll be able to relax more at home, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.40,0:03:16.09,apollon main,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}I don't mind, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.04,0:03:21.61,apollon main,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}She might overhear us if we discuss our plans in the basement.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.58,0:03:23.64,apollon main,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Here it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.40,0:03:26.51,apollon main,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,This is Ri's shop.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.51,0:03:29.48,apollon main,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,We live in a row house, so our places are connected.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.99,0:03:32.81,apollon main,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Ma!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.81,0:03:34.15,apollon main,Kota,0000,0000,0000,,Bro!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.15,0:03:36.80,apollon main,Sachiko,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome home, Bro! You're \Nback early today, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.80,0:03:38.14,apollon main,Kota,0000,0000,0000,,Play with us!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.14,0:03:40.70,apollon main,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on, hold on. Where's Ma?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.70,0:03:43.45,apollon main,Sachiko,0000,0000,0000,,Ma, Bro's home!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.07,0:03:42.88,apollon main,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Richie!{alt}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.45,0:03:46.20,apollon main,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,What're you doin'? Come on in.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.62,0:03:54.20,apollon main,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Ma, this is Richie.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.20,0:03:55.92,apollon main,Ma,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, hello there.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.92,0:03:58.26,apollon main,Ma,0000,0000,0000,,I appreciate you always looking out for Sentaro.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.95,0:04:01.31,apollon main,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you're too kind.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.82,0:04:04.84,apollon main,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be shy. Dig in, Richie.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.65,0:04:10.34,apollon main,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,I thought you didn't have an appetite today.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.34,0:04:11.80,apollon main,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,I can {\i1}always{\i0}{\fscx125} {\fscx100}eat watermelon.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.80,0:04:14.86,apollon main,Ma,0000,0000,0000,,Sentaro loves his watermelon.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.73,0:04:19.41,apollon main,Ma,0000,0000,0000,,He told me he wasn't feeling hungry, which is unusual for him,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.41,0:04:23.37,apollon main,Ma,0000,0000,0000,,but I had a hunch he'd be able to eat some watermelon, so I iced one up.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.29,0:04:26.37,apollon main,Taichi,0000,0000,0000,,Bro! Bro!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.36,0:04:27.78,apollon main,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,What's up, Taichi?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.78,0:04:29.59,apollon main,Taichi,0000,0000,0000,,We found a weird bug!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.59,0:04:30.58,apollon main,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,A bug?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.58,0:04:31.58,apollon main,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Is it a big one?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.58,0:04:32.58,apollon main,Taichi,0000,0000,0000,,It's over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.58,0:04:36.07,apollon main,Kota,0000,0000,0000,,Bro, if you plant a watermelon seed, will it grow?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.07,0:04:37.33,apollon main,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Let's plant one an' see.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.33,0:04:38.86,apollon main,Kota,0000,0000,0000,,Look, there!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.09,0:04:39.84,apollon main,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, there it is!{alt}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.38,0:04:41.86,apollon main,Kota,0000,0000,0000,,It flew!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.86,0:04:44.81,apollon main,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Yeesh, don't cry about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.34,0:04:48.10,apollon main,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,A group date?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.10,0:04:52.48,apollon main,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. Ri and I will tag along.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.48,0:04:55.22,apollon main,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,She'll be on guard if you start with just the two of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.22,0:04:58.03,apollon main,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.03,0:05:00.61,apollon main,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, you'll be the one to invite Miss Yurika.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.18,0:05:03.59,apollon main,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,What's the point if you're \Nnot the one who does it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.59,0:05:06.67,apollon main,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,I can't! I just don't have it in me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.67,0:05:08.08,apollon main,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Look...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.64,0:05:10.83,apollon main,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,What's that sound?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.83,0:05:11.96,apollon main,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Sarah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.96,0:05:13.11,apollon main,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Sarah?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.11,0:05:14.29,apollon main,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,My girlfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.29,0:05:15.15,apollon main,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.60,0:05:18.33,apollon main,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Sarah?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.16,0:05:20.84,apollon main,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,You're in a bad mood.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.30,0:05:22.93,apollon main,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Cute, ain't she?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.93,0:05:24.98,apollon main,,0000,0000,0000,,Her full name is Sarah Vaughan.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.98,0:05:26.44,apollon main,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,A pigeon, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.67,0:05:29.17,apollon main,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,What is it, Sarah?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.17,0:05:30.72,apollon main,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,You're lookin' upset today.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.72,0:05:32.91,apollon main,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,She's probably jealous.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.91,0:05:35.69,apollon main,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,You've been talking about another girl, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.95,0:05:43.36,apollon main,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.15,0:05:46.62,apollon main,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,When did I start enjoying myself?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.20,0:05:51.95,apollon main,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,That was so funny!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.95,0:05:52.91,apollon main,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.31,0:05:57.33,apollon main,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.95,0:06:00.07,apollon main,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,U-Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.75,0:06:06.35,apollon main,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,I-Idiot! Who goes up to the girl and then runs away?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.35,0:06:07.81,apollon main,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,I can't do it, man!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.81,0:06:08.72,apollon main,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Remember the note!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.72,0:06:10.01,apollon main,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.92,0:06:12.51,apollon main,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,He's coming back.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.03,0:06:15.30,apollon main,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.56,0:06:20.06,apollon main,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,for suddenly interrupting you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.64,0:06:24.20,apollon main,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Are you free this weekend?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.40,0:06:31.21,apollon main,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,I would like to take this opportunity to cult... cult...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.21,0:06:32.41,apollon main,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,"Cultivate."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.41,0:06:35.18,apollon main,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,cultivate... our friendship!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.45,0:06:35.18,apollon main,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,That idiot.{alt}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.35,0:06:38.85,apollon main,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Richie! Richie!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.85,0:06:41.03,apollon main,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,She said yes! She's goin' with us!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.81,0:06:44.94,apollon main,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to Rendezvous Rock, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.94,0:06:46.80,apollon main,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,Shall I pack us a lunch?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.61,0:06:50.91,apollon main,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Um, that'd be great.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.91,0:06:53.54,apollon main,,0000,0000,0000,,Something light like onigiri would be good.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.54,0:06:55.99,apollon main,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, leave it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.99,0:06:59.06,apollon main,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, just so I know,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.65,0:07:03.56,apollon main,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,which one of you is inviting me?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.55,0:07:05.57,apollon main,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that would be...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.45,0:07:09.95,apollon main,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,This guy! He insisted on inviting you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.95,0:07:11.28,apollon main,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.30,0:07:13.07,apollon main,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.42,0:07:14.96,apollon main,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.96,0:07:17.58,apollon main,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I'm looking forward to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.58,0:07:19.21,apollon main,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,You agreed to go on a date?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.21,0:07:20.31,apollon main,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.08,0:07:23.67,apollon main,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,You really are a fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.67,0:07:26.79,apollon main,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,It was going smooth as can be, and then you blew it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.79,0:07:30.31,apollon main,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I dunno why I said that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.02,0:07:33.64,apollon main,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Wind back time for me, Richie!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.64,0:07:34.80,apollon main,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,As if I can!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.18,0:07:39.56,apollon main,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry to keep you waiting!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.90,0:07:41.92,apollon main,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, there's Kaoru!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.35,0:07:45.98,apollon main,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what happened to your face?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.98,0:07:48.57,apollon main,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Just another one of his fights.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.31,0:07:50.82,apollon main,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go, Kaoru.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.42,0:07:54.99,apollon main,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Wait a minute, Ri. One more person will be joining us today.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.99,0:07:56.12,apollon main,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.12,0:07:57.38,apollon main,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,I'm late!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.91,0:08:01.28,apollon main,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,Making lunch took longer than I thought it would.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.73,0:08:07.38,apollon main,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,You're the girl those hooligans were harassing at the beach.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.38,0:08:08.05,apollon main,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Th-That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.54,0:08:11.23,apollon main,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,You remember her, huh? Actually, today...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.38,0:08:14.90,apollon main,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Get a hold of yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.90,0:08:17.49,apollon main,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,The one with the glasses invited me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.38,0:08:18.35,apollon main,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Are you all right?! Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.35,0:08:19.56,apollon main,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Kaoru invited you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.56,0:08:20.96,apollon main,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.56,0:08:22.35,apollon main,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}What the heck are you doing?! Hey?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.96,0:08:24.53,apollon main,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,Is it okay for a newcomer like me to intrude?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.99,0:08:24.53,apollon main,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Get up already!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.53,0:08:28.19,apollon main,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,O-Oh, of course. The more the merrier!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.58,0:08:28.19,apollon main,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}What's wrong with you today?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.19,0:08:30.07,apollon main,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,Really? Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.45,0:08:33.61,apollon main,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, so it was Kaoru that asked her.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.94,0:08:42.50,apollon main,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,She's beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.38,0:08:45.79,apollon main,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Kaoru must have a weakness for pretty faces.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.31,0:08:47.63,apollon main,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.63,0:08:51.04,apollon main,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing. I was just thinking that your hat is really stylish.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.04,0:08:52.55,apollon main,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, this?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.40,0:08:56.00,apollon main,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Even if I wore it, I'd still look like a yokel.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.00,0:08:58.05,apollon main,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that's not true.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.05,0:08:59.81,apollon main,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,Pardon me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.60,0:09:08.06,apollon main,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Ri, when did you change your hairstyle?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.67,0:09:11.63,apollon main,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Yurika did it for me. What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.63,0:09:14.07,apollon main,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,It looks super. Really cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.01,0:09:25.08,apollon main,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that's right. I'm told your family owns a record shop, Ritsuko.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.60,0:09:29.08,apollon main,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. Do you like jazz, Yurika?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.14,0:09:35.04,apollon main,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,These two practice playing it together just about every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.04,0:09:36.53,apollon main,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,They play jazz?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.55,0:09:41.54,apollon main,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Yup. Kaoru plays piano, and Sentaro plays the drums.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.54,0:09:45.33,apollon main,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,That's really something! I know \Nsome people who listen to jazz,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.33,0:09:46.85,apollon main,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,but this is my first time meeting anyone who actually plays it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.29,0:09:50.83,apollon main,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,My two big brothers like jazz, \Nso I listen too once in a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.83,0:09:54.69,apollon main,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,They frown and get a wrinkle between their eyebrows when they listen,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.69,0:09:56.61,apollon main,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,but I prefer music that really hits you with a bang, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.15,0:09:59.70,apollon main,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! That's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.70,0:10:02.08,apollon main,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,I'd love to hear you play the drums.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.08,0:10:08.62,apollon main,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You can't! I still, uh... stink at it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.62,0:10:12.96,apollon main,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, but you know you can't improve unless you have an audience, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.96,0:10:14.63,apollon main,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, let me hear you play.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.32,0:10:18.28,apollon main,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,This... is an unexpected development.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.28,0:10:19.26,apollon main,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.63,0:10:22.66,apollon main,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no! I think I got scratched by a branch.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.02,0:10:31.30,apollon main,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Well, what do you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.30,0:10:33.05,apollon main,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like he's got some moves after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.11,0:10:41.78,apollon main,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, I heard a rumor that couples who climb to the top of that rock together will get married.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.05,0:10:45.04,apollon main,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,No girl's gonna get up that!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.04,0:10:46.95,apollon main,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Richie, you up for it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.95,0:10:48.16,apollon main,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Why me?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.44,0:10:51.14,apollon main,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I'm not letting you get away with saying that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.14,0:10:53.13,apollon main,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,I can make it that high.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.89,0:10:55.67,apollon main,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,Would anyone like to go with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.63,0:10:58.26,apollon main,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Go on!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.56,0:11:00.09,apollon main,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,N-No!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.11,0:11:08.02,apollon main,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, the sign says it's off limits... and it's dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.39,0:11:12.84,apollon main,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that's too bad. I really wanted \Nto see the view from up there.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.35,0:11:21.97,apollon main,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,You shouldn't have wolfed it down!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.26,0:11:27.42,apollon main,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Those two seem to be getting on well.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.45,0:11:31.94,apollon main,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Kaoru, you can have this.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.74,0:11:34.04,apollon main,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.44,0:11:36.13,apollon main,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just going to pick some flowers!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.35,0:11:39.43,apollon main,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Probably the bathroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.85,0:11:45.10,apollon main,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Boy, this onigiri is huge.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.25,0:12:08.66,apollon main,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,It's my fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.97,0:12:12.08,apollon main,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,I hurt her...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.85,0:12:15.03,apollon main,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,in the cruelest of ways.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.02,0:12:20.09,apollon main,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,I made the girl who's most important to me cry.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.41,0:12:24.09,apollon main,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Those shoulders look so sad, but I have no right...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.27,0:12:26.63,apollon main,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,to try and comfort her.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.27,0:12:39.86,apollon main,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning, Kaoru.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.22,0:12:42.22,apollon main,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.22,0:12:42.93,apollon main,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Richie!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.86,0:12:45.72,apollon main,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,C-Come with me a sec!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.62,0:12:49.62,apollon main,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Look! This handkerchief!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.02,0:12:53.62,apollon main,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Yurika gave it to me as an apology for my towel yesterday!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.63,0:12:57.25,apollon main,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,It smells kind of nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.84,0:12:59.50,apollon main,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Or is it my imagination?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.03,0:13:06.01,apollon main,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell was that for?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.84,0:13:11.99,apollon main,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Kaoru?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.56,0:13:14.98,apollon main,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't let you pick up this handkerchief!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.98,0:13:16.86,apollon main,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't bear seeing that!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.55,0:13:26.28,apollon main,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,If you're here for the handkerchief, you can have it back.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.75,0:13:28.64,apollon main,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,I was in the wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.64,0:13:30.47,apollon main,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,It's all my fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.47,0:13:32.95,apollon main,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,What're you talkin' about? Tell me already!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.95,0:13:34.15,apollon main,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.15,0:13:37.05,apollon main,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,You're satisfied as long as you have this handkerchief, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.05,0:13:39.84,apollon main,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Go home and sniff it all you want!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.70,0:13:41.80,apollon main,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,That's enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.41,0:13:43.80,apollon main,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,You lookin' to start a fight?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.22,0:13:48.18,apollon main,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.18,0:13:51.35,apollon main,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Sentaro, let go of Kaoru!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.40,0:13:55.35,apollon main,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,This is stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.69,0:13:57.07,apollon main,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Don't get rough with him!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.07,0:13:58.72,apollon main,,0000,0000,0000,,You owe him an apology!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.94,0:14:02.36,apollon main,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,I don't owe that guy nothin'.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.76,0:14:04.10,apollon main,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, Sentaro!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.00,0:14:08.37,apollon main,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,You can't forget this.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.64,0:14:12.20,apollon main,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,This handkerchief is important to you, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.02,0:14:19.71,apollon main,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Kaoru,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.49,0:14:24.67,apollon main,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}I bet Sentaro is drumming away \Nlike a madman right about now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.45,0:14:27.43,apollon main,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Richie, you stupid idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.43,0:14:27.92,apollon main,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.41,0:14:32.08,apollon main,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}The sooner you make up, the easier it'll be.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.67,0:14:34.04,apollon main,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Come with me to practice.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.04,0:14:35.14,apollon main,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.14,0:14:40.44,apollon main,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Before you moved here, Sentaro always practiced alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.38,0:14:43.94,apollon main,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Shutting himself in the basement, \Nnot letting anyone near him...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.99,0:14:47.69,apollon main,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Even I didn't feel welcome in the basement.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.25,0:14:52.91,apollon main,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,But ever since you came, that feeling's been gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.91,0:14:56.77,apollon main,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,I'm positive he's happy that he found a friend to play with.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.51,0:15:02.71,apollon main,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Kaoru, shall I guess what you \Ntwo were fighting about today?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.26,0:15:06.84,apollon main,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,You like Yurika, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.22,0:15:11.72,apollon main,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,I bet you got mad at Sentaro for showing off that handkerchief.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.44,0:15:14.83,apollon main,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,She is really pretty.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.61,0:15:18.98,apollon main,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,I wish I'd been born looking like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.98,0:15:22.13,apollon main,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.13,0:15:23.90,apollon main,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Ri, you're plenty...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.33,0:15:26.42,apollon main,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,a-attractive.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.27,0:15:33.16,apollon main,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for trying to cheer me up.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.75,0:15:36.54,apollon main,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not... I wasn't...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.54,0:15:39.48,apollon main,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,I wasn't trying to cheer you up. I...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.67,0:15:43.04,apollon main,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Here we are!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.63,0:15:45.04,apollon main,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Well, good luck!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.15,0:15:48.26,apollon main,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Ri! Open up!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.18,0:15:51.69,apollon main,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Let me out, Ri!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.65,0:15:51.69,apollon main,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,What's the ruckus, Ritsuko?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.72,0:15:54.01,apollon main,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Drastic measures.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.76,0:15:59.77,apollon main,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,I-I didn't come here to see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.62,0:16:07.48,apollon main,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.41,0:16:10.49,apollon main,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,N-Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.79,0:16:18.27,apollon main,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,He feels the same way about the girl he likes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.99,0:16:32.39,apollon main,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, don't just join in!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.39,0:16:32.92,apollon main,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.98,0:16:35.34,apollon main,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,I wasn't tryin' to join in.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.62,0:16:46.23,apollon main,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,He's following along again.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.67,0:16:59.99,apollon main,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.99,0:17:01.16,apollon main,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Jazz with a festival dance beat!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.16,0:17:04.03,apollon main,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Cut it out! I can't play if I'm laughing!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.71,0:17:41.15,apollon main,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Next time, maybe I'll play \Nsomething just for Ri.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.84,0:17:47.30,apollon main,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,And then... maybe I'll try letting her know how I feel.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.72,0:17:53.96,apollon main,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,Sentaro.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.55,0:17:55.92,apollon main,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,I'm coming in.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.72,0:18:01.18,apollon main,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, don't be so stiff.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.39,0:18:09.23,apollon main,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,What the...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.49,0:18:11.90,apollon main,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,hell is he doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.65,0:18:19.53,apollon main,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure Ri is thinking about him.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.70,0:18:25.54,apollon main,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,310)}Meanwhile, he's...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.79,0:18:30.08,apollon main,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Um, Ri...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.57,0:18:34.59,apollon main,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,There's a song that I'd like to play for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.87,0:18:40.17,apollon main,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,I've been practicing my heart out on this song.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.05,0:18:45.77,apollon main,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,I wish I still had more time to work on it,\Nbut I feel like I have to play this for her now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.41,0:18:50.02,apollon main,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Play through me, Bill Evans.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.70,0:20:16.29,apollon main,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,"Someday My Prince Will Come."
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.04,0:20:19.15,apollon main,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,That's the title of the song.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.32,0:20:24.16,apollon main,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,So you're the prince?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.57,0:20:25.88,apollon main,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,I'm right, aren't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.88,0:20:29.16,apollon main,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,You've been practicing for Yurika, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.71,0:20:32.05,apollon main,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,And this is your "dress rehearsal"!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.94,0:20:33.92,apollon main,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.08,0:20:40.77,apollon main,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,This is the real performance.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.51,0:20:45.47,apollon main,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,You're the one that I like.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.29,0:20:50.77,apollon main,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have to give me an answer right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.35,0:20:55.73,apollon main,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,I just wanted to let you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.25,0:20:58.74,apollon main,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,that there's somebody here who's in love with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.94,0:21:06.27,apollon main,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Ri's eyes are on him.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.26,0:21:10.43,apollon main,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,She's always thinking of him.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.68,0:21:13.58,apollon main,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,That doesn't bother me though.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.70,0:21:19.86,apollon main,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,You taught me that it was possible to fall in love like this.
